				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">Build Your AI Email Agent with Copilot Studio</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 line-clamp-2">A comprehensive tutorial on how to create an AI agent that can send emails on your behalf using Microsoft Copilot Studio and robust backend tools.</p>
				<span class="text-indigo-600 text-sm font-medium flex items-center">
					Read Article <span class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
				</span>
			</a>
			<!-- Article Card 3 -->
			<a href="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/blog/azurecommunicationservicesblog/build-an-ai-email-responder-with-openai-and-azure-communication-services/4421127" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block p-6 rounded-xl bg-white border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-indigo-100 transition-all">
				<div class="text-xs font-semibold text-indigo-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Article &bull; Microsoft Tech Community</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">Build an AI Email Responder with OpenAI & Azure</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 line-clamp-2">Learn how to automate customer support and repetitive queries using OpenAI and Azure Communication Services in this detailed guide.</p>
				<span class="text-indigo-600 text-sm font-medium flex items-center">
					Read Article <span class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
				</span>
			</a>
